data.description: ***PRICE IMPROVEMENT*** Turn your dreams into reality with this charming home! This home is almost BRAND NEW as it’s only 1 year old! From the moment you step onto the welcoming front porch, you'll know you've found something special. This delightful three-bedroom, two-bathroom home boasts vaulted ceilings and an open, airy floor plan that makes living here effortless. This home offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience with its inviting porch, spacious interior, and proximity to both city amenities and natural wonders. The luxury of the soft wood flooring extends throughout and adds a touch of warmth and elegance to every room. You'll also appreciate the convenience of an inside laundry area, making daily chores a breeze. Situated on a spacious lot, this home offers an open porch where you can enjoy outdoor activities with family and friends. Whether it's a barbecue, a game of catch, or simply basking in the Florida sunshine, this outdoor space is perfect for creating lasting memories. Conveniently close to High Springs, Gainesville or Lake City, and a few minutes away from some of the best springs in Florida.
